{"tid":2051716,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"岑子杰：不少瀝源邨學童家長感憂心 冀繼續停課","createTime":"2020-06-05T03:39:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-05T03:46:10.000Z","uid":166360,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6e0ae5f020d3861b8070e107186d9f70d0ec5e70","tid":2051716,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T03:39:41.000Z","msg":"岑子杰：不少瀝源邨學童家長感憂心 冀繼續停課<br />\n2020-06-05 HKT 10:45<br />\n<br />\n沙田瀝源邨祿泉樓至今累計有7宗新型肺炎確診個案，當局昨日緊急撤離部分居民。<br />\n<br />\n屬瀝源選區的沙田區議員岑子杰在本台節目《千禧年代》批評，當局的撤離指示不清晰，對於安排撤離時不在家的居民，並無留下任何聯絡方法，其他仍然留在祿泉樓的居民，則認為當局的措施無法令他們安心繼續居住。<br />\n<br />\n岑子杰又說，瀝源邨附近有6至7間中小學，不少學童家長都向他反映，由於擔心出現社區傳播，因此希望可以繼續停課。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1530315-20200605.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1530315-20200605.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=OUx24mKaoEPTVTG9WcU5EmbkIIQgOyZVEIOEDwMYbAQ%3D&h=4e7683ec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1530315-20200605.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=aad48fd1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1530315-20200605.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"eb0ee2b1098e8e16bb58c997b7cdfbffa735b0f3","tid":2051716,"uid":37487,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T03:41:22.000Z","msg":"停課係圈套黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a50f19ade340efd8bdff51bd738278b23623faf","tid":2051716,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T03:42:33.000Z","msg":"恐懼撚煩到死"},{"pid":"4232998dc561cf6d0c231225c54a0a5d5e76b55b","tid":2051716,"uid":186174,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7a50f19ade340efd8bdff51bd738278b23623faf","tid":2051716,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T03:42:33.000Z","msg":"恐懼撚煩到死"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T03:44: